pacman::p_load(ggiraph, plotly,
               patchwork, DT, tidyverse)
exam_data_2 <- read_csv("C:/calvintansh/ISSS608-VAA/Hands-on_Ex/Hands-on_Ex03-1/data/Exam_data.csv")
library(htmltools)

d <- highlight_key(exam_data_2)
p <- ggplot(d,
            aes(ENGLISH,
                MATHS)) +
  geom_point(size = 1) +
  coord_cartesian(xlim = c(0,100),
                  ylim = c(0,100))

gg <- highlight(
  ggplotly(p) %>% layout(height = 300, width = 300),
  "plotly_selected"
)

crosstalk::bscols(
  widths = 12,
  div(style = "height: 300px; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;", gg),
  DT::datatable(d, 
                class = "compact",
                options = list(pageLength = 5))
)
library(htmltools)

d <- highlight_key(exam_data_2)
p <- ggplot(d,
            aes(ENGLISH,
                MATHS)) +
  geom_point(size = 1) +
  coord_cartesian(xlim = c(0,100),
                  ylim = c(0,100))

gg <- highlight(
  ggplotly(p, width = 300, height = 300) %>% 
    layout(autosize = FALSE),   # <- THIS prevents auto-stretching
  "plotly_selected"
)

crosstalk::bscols(
  widths = 12,
  div(style = "height: 300px; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;", gg),
  DT::datatable(d, 
                class = "compact",
                options = list(pageLength = 5))
)
